        Description copied from interface: Supplier
        Returns the contents of this object in this particular moment. For memoryless nodes, this may involve a costly recomputation of contents.

        Intended mainly for debug purposes, therefore does not do flushing. During runtime, flushing may be preferred; see ReteContainer.pullContents(Supplier)
